---
title: Homemade Apple Beef Burgers with crispy chips and crunchy salad
description: Grated apple provides an easy way to add taste and texture to a burger. Perfectly crispy chips and a fresh cucumber side salad are also welcome additions to this dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R02_W04_IE_IEXCFB0086-2_KB_Main_high-9683e5be.jpg
